      • valueToMatch

        String valueToMatch()
        Return the path segment value to use for pattern matching purposes. By default this is the same as PathContainer.Element.value() but may also differ in sub-interfaces (e.g. decoded, sanitized, etc.).

      • valueToMatchAsChars

        char[] valueToMatchAsChars()
        The same as valueToMatch() but as a char[].
